{"tid":1777050,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"是日風向，唱衰香港等於政治暴發戶","createTime":"2019-12-10T03:00:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-10T03:52:24.000Z","uid":172427,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4a9cf1dfd3fd0aac500edd6e7085039fdf6fdfc7","tid":1777050,"uid":172427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T03:00:31.000Z","msg":"先係分化港台，再屈佢地係政治暴發戶<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】行政長官林鄭月娥主持行政會議前見記者，她指會致力維護基本人權，不願看到有人去外國「唱衰香港」。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥又回應周日的遊行，她形容是大致有序，特區政府尊重表達自由，警方亦表現克制，又指過去幾個月無論遊行人數多少，特區政府都用心聆聽，撤回逃犯條例修訂已直接回應訴求，至於其他訴求包括特赦被捕人士，因偏離法治原則難以辦到。"},{"pid":"7c20d3b3834bd4f79bcd6adb4aa2bf64a7dc5fc8","tid":1777050,"uid":172427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T03:00:45.000Z","msg":"1/10 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8d3ca6a0235a2d925163eed5f298db5015bb8f0","tid":1777050,"uid":172427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T03:00:57.000Z","msg":"2/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9c739354f81509b8903f0ba2188ebc8ce797195","tid":1777050,"uid":172427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T03:01:13.000Z","msg":"3/10 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fff7b077a54e6f6b56249f61d8f8f4f471165056","tid":1777050,"uid":172427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T03:01:26.000Z","msg":"4/10 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal